rows.label: qst104702_msg001
rows.name:
あれはスペルビアから 避難する人たちを乗せた船だよ
ここからグーラに向かうんだってさ(仮)

rows.label: qst104702_msg002
rows.name: 護衛もつけてるらしいけど 最近は何かと物騒だから心配だなあ(仮)

rows.label: qst104702_msg003
rows.name: キミ 良かったらグーラに行って 様子を見てきてくれないか？(仮)

rows.label: qst104702_msg0001
rows.name:
Still no sign of the
ship from Superbia...

rows.label: qst104702_msg0002
rows.name: It was due to arrive ages ago.

rows.label: qst104702_msg0003
rows.name:
They have a resupply scheduled in
Yeshiva Harbor, over Liberalitas way.
I wonder if they made it that far?

rows.label: qst104702_msg0004
rows.name:
Would you mind checking for me?
It'd be a weight off my mind!

rows.label: qst104702_msg0005
rows.name:
I hope it's just run-of-the-mill
delays and nothing more serious...

rows.label: qst104702_msg0101
rows.name:
There's been an increase
lately in the number of
people leaving the capital.

rows.label: qst104702_msg0102
rows.name:
Not sure we'd be able to house the
entire Empire if they all decided to
come here. Hope it all works out...
